# 🌱 Urban Farming Platform — Backend System

> Production-ready backend for an interactive urban farming ecosystem  
> Enabling farm rental, organic marketplace, plant tracking, and community collaboration.

---

## 🎯 Overview

This system connects **urban users, farmers, and eco-enthusiasts** into a unified platform where users can:

- Rent farming spaces
- Buy/sell organic produce
- Track plant growth in real-time
- Share knowledge via community forum

👉 Built with scalability, performance, and real-world constraints in mind.

---

## 🧠 Core Capabilities

### 🔐 Authentication & Access Control
- JWT + Refresh Token
- Role-based access (Admin, Vendor, Customer)

### 🏠 Farm Rental System
- Location-based search
- Booking & availability management

### 🛒 Marketplace
- Vendor product management
- Order lifecycle (create → process → complete)

### 🌱 Plant Tracking
- Growth stage monitoring
- Health updates & harvest alerts (real-time)

### 💬 Community Forum
- Post, comment, and engagement system

### ✅ Sustainability Verification
- Vendor certification workflow
- Admin validation system

---

## ⚙️ Tech Stack

- **Backend:** Node.js, Express, TypeScript  
- **Database:** PostgreSQL + Prisma  
- **Cache:** Redis  
- **Realtime:** Socket.IO  
- **Validation:** Zod  
- **Auth:** JWT  
- **Docs:** Swagger / Postman  

---

## 🏗 Architecture Highlights

- Modular structure (feature-based modules)
- Global error handling
- Standardized API response format
- Rate limiting for sensitive routes
- Redis caching for high-frequency endpoints
- Indexed DB queries for performance

